name: Released
description:
A droplet hangs from a newly bloomed Lilac floret. The Lilac is a symbol of early growth, renewal, confidence, first love, magic and the transition from innocence to wisdom.(Syringa vulgaris) 

This piece is a gift and thank you to all of my collectors in 2021 as well as community builders and artists who think highly of.

It has been an incredible few months, and this token is a reflection of my appreciation for your support of myself and the community at large!

2019. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.

1024x685 300dpi jpeg
